        "type": "mcq",
        "stem": "<p   dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Find the point of inflection of the curve </span><span class=\"LexicalTheme__math--inline\" data-node-type=\"math\" data-node-variation=\"inline\"><math-field default-mode=\"inline-math\" read-only=\"true\" value=\"y=3x^2+5x+6\" locale=\"en\">y=3x^2+5x+6</math-field></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> .</span></p>",
